Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:05.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:13.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:33.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:36.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:44.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:47.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:50.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:56.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:01:01.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:05.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:16.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.07,0:01:21.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:24.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:28.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.29,0:01:37.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.34,0:01:41.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize what you have done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.25,0:01:43.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.63,0:01:47.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This was broadcast nationwide\Nthe other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:49.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nationwide!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:51.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:56.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how much dishonor\Nyou brought upon this school
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:01:58.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,with the airing of this footage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:01:59.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.17,0:02:02.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki and Kuchiki were on television,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:05.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so I can understand why they\Nwere called in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:08.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no reason\Nwhy Inoue and I should be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:11.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:12.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:16.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We met them by accident\Nand were not involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:17.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.29,0:02:19.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to save your own necks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:24.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And so, we're going back to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:25.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Orihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:30.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...then me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:32.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:35.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You were with him,\Nbut did nothing to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:36.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're just as guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's the fuss\Njust 'cuz we were on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:42.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"Just 'cuz"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:44.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you realized that\Nyou're here precisely
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,because of that lack of\Nawareness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:47.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm flabbergasted!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:49.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:52.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:56.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't stop Kurosaki who was\Nso determined to get on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:02:58.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:02.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I really tried my best, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:05.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh... Don't cry, Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:07.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.\NIt's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:11.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what you do to Kurasaki,\Nso please spare me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:12.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:14.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:19.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what will happen\Nif you run away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:20.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:22.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And now, even Kuchiki has disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:24.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Principal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:26.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, you don't have to\Nscold them so severely,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:28.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,just because they\Nwere on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:38.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All's well that end's well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you, Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:43.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh please...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:45.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid, don't compliment her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She tried to sell me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:52.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to her act,\Nyou were able to slip away, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:53.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:55.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was just an a…c…t.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:04:01.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn’t dream of selling out\Na friend like Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:02.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:09.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Kurosaki,\Nmay I speak with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:10.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:13.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse us, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:17.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki and Kuchiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:21.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:24.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are they seeing each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:27.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At least, Kuchiki wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:31.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But something's suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:39.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:46.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:51.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that cell phone\Nis broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:52.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:56.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There was an order that\Na Hollow had appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:04:59.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:03.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't exterminate\Na Hollow by any chance, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:07.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hollow...you mean that\Nscary bug-like thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:11.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was so scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was\Ngonna pee on myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:15.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:17.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:20.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone defeat\Nthe Hollow and save you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And if so, who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:31.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was so scared,\NI had my eyes closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:32.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:33.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:34.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:36.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's Konso time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:37.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:40.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What's a Konso?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:42.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that sword for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:09.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Third place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You always do so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:17.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Orihime,\Nyou're that smart?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:20.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't look it though, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:21.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are my Hime, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:25.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:27.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, besides the girls doing well,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:32.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,no one betrayed us by getting into\Nthe top 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:34.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:35.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:40.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:43.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,23rd place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:47.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:48.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:52.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I study because there's nothing\Nelse to do at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:54.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to do?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:56.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I always ask you to hang out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:57.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:00.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you were doing\Nwhen you turned me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:03.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert! Nerd!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:06.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A person like you deserves\Nthick glasses like these--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:07.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:10.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you actually study, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:12.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:15.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It can be tough when you\Nhave orange hair like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:19.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I guess there are\Nall kinds of things in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:22.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A person like you deserves\Na nerd headband--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:24.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:29.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never ask you to hang out again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:32.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Chad, c'mon and join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:34.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're not in the top fifty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:36.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:39.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:42.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I never thought you guys were so evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:47.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never play with you guys again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh...you made him cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:53.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we're evil, what about\Nthe guy who's number one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:56.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ametatsu Ishida?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:07:58.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never heard of that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:07:59.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's Uryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:01.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uryu Ishida.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:02.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's in our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:05.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it, Orihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:10.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He never remembers\Na person's name or face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:11.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:14.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... was there such a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:19.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:21.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Urahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:24.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you answer when I call\Nyou at times like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:28.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You always show up when\Nyou're not needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:31.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself a businessman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:35.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:39.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted him to take\Na look at my Soul Pager.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:43.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell if it's broken or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:51.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:52.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go sing some karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:53.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The worker there--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:54.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:56.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:59.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia is quite aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:02.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think they really are\Nseeing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:04.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:07.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow? I hope it's really\Nthere this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:08.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:16.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:30.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,After all this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:33.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There was no Hollow again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:35.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:36.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get back into your body now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:38.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:41.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do something about that\Nuseless cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:43.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that it's my fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:48.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just relay whatever comes\Nthrough the Soul Pager.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:52.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So hurry it up and fix that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:54.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:56.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:04.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How unsightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:08.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, Kurosaki...Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:10.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:12.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know our names?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:16.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki, you can\Nsee spirits, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:20.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.29,0:10:23.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A new Hollow has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:24.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:30.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's right. It's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:31.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:35.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:41.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know such a basic thing\Nand you call yourself a Soul Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:10:58.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:15.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:18.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just what are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:24.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uryu Ishida. A Quincy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:28.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hate Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:29.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:30.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:35.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you...\NIchigo Kurosaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:55.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Just what is that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:59.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know such a basic thing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and you call yourself a Soul Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:07.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to\Nbe insulted like that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:09.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,by someone I met for\Nthe first time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:13.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get that bastard\Nthe next time we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:19.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...what did he say his\Nname was?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:24.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida... err... Willy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. That's that celebrity\Nno one likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:27.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:33.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue! Oh...no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:35.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uryu Ishida, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:36.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:39.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah him! You're well informed, Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:41.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:44.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But Ishida and I are in\Nthe Handicrafts Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:45.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I know his name,\Nat least.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:46.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Handicrafts Club?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:50.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See? That's Ishida.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:00.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And he's in the Handicrafts Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:06.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Conveniently, Michiru brought\Na torn stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:09.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Very convenient turn of events indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:10.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:34.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fixed! Thank you, Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:36.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:38.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:43.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:47.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He'd be nice if he didn't\Nsay things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:50.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:53.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:56.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen\Nbetween you and him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just something minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:13:59.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:01.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:24.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You plan on following me home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:29.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:32.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When did you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:38.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From the time you and Inoue\Nwatched me from the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:41.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:42.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:46.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your spiritual energy is\Nalways leaking out, like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:48.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even a monkey would notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:50.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:56.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're lacking the ability\Nto detect those with high spiritual energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:14:58.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The proof lies in the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:01.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that you didn't notice\Nmy existence until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:07.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.\NI'm bad at remembering people's faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:11.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From the time you entered school
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:16.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that you had unusually high\Nspiritual energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:22.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Also, that you became a Soul Reaper\Naround the middle of May.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:26.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And...I know Rukia Kuchiki's\Ntrue identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:35.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Ribbons!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:38.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Spirit Ribbons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:41.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The compression and manifestation\Nof spiritual energy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:42.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:43.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:49.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:51.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your Spirit Ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:58.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:01.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers' Spirit Ribbons have\Ndifferent colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:11.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let us duel, Ichigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You or me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:16.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you who is\Nthe stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:21.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And also, that Soul Reapers\Naren't necessary in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:25.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Urahara Store\N		It's a duel! Rock, Paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:26.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:29.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look away, then show!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, Paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:32.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:34.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look away, then show!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:40.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's your turn\Nto sweep, Jinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:42.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't lost yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:46.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's two out of three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:51.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You never said that! Never! Owwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:53.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oweee!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:55.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quit complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:57.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One more time, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:04.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What...are you doing, Jinta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:08.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,3\Nm\N		e\N		t\N		e\N		r\N		s\N		Oh...nothing...Te…Eh…Mr.Tessai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:14.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:18.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You have some business today, Kuchiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:20.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:23.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is Urahara here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:26.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:28.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do for you–?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:31.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"What can I do for you"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:34.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I called you time and time again,\Nbut you never answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:36.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I've come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:41.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We've been quite busy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.13,0:17:46.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what happened to\Nthat spiky-haired guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:51.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't like him,\Nso it's better that he stayed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Jinta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I need to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:57.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:01.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A duel? You and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:03.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:13.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:15.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:18.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to do such\Na stupid thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:22.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what kind of grudge\Nyou have against Soul Reapers,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:24.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but it’s got nothing\Nto do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:26.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:27.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to get out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to goad me into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:32.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it would be no contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:35.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I just remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:40.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're a Soul Reaper who received\Nyour powers from Kuchiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:43.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're a substitute Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:49.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Without her authority,\Nyou can’t even lift a finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:54.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quincy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:57.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard that name\Nin a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:01.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It has a nostalgic ring to it,\Ndoesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:05.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's been nearly 200 years\Nsince we heard that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:07.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:10.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quincy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:12.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A tribe which once existed scattered\Nthroughout the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.97,0:19:16.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,which specialized in destroying Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:19.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They became extinct about\N200 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:22.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Extinct?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:29.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Humans who had powers like\NKurosaki sensed the existence of Hollows
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:32.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and began to train\Nto fight against them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:33.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that's how the tribe started.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:36.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like Soul Reapers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:37.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,their mission was to\Ndestroy Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:41.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, there was one\Ndistinct difference
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:42.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,between them\Nand Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:47.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And that was, whether to\Nkill Hollows or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:50.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Soul Reapers seek to purify\NHollows with their Zanpaku-to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:53.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and allow them to cross over\Ninto the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:58.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But Quincys sought to totally kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:12.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When you think about it,\Nit was a very human thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:15.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hollows devour human souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:18.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They hurt and kill\Nour friends and family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:22.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So why would you want to send them\Nto the Soul Society peacefully?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:25.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was only natural that\Nthey opposed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:29.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So they always tried to kill Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:33.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They believed that they were\Navenging their comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:39.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But due to that belief,\Nthey were destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:43.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.79,0:20:47.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it.\NWe'll have a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:49.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:50.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:53.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You may've been obeying Rukia's orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:57.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but how dare you stuff me in\Nthat bag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:20:59.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:01.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! Not again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:06.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:09.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Slimy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:19.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kon, watch me.
